<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>@ViewBag.Title</title>
    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .navbar {
            background-color: #0a3d62;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1320px;
        }

        .navbar-brand {
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .navbar-nav .nav-link {
            color: #fff;
        }

        .hero {
            margin-top: 100px;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 50px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }

            .hero h1 {
                color: #0a3d62;
                font-size: 3rem;
                font-weight: bold;
            }

            .hero p {
                color: black;
                font-size: 1.2rem;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }

        .search-form {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

            .search-form .form-control {
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #1e90ff;
            border: none;
        }

            .btn-primary:hover {
                background-color: #1c86ee;
            }

        .gif-container {
            margin-top: -60px;
            text-align: center;
        }

            .gif-container img {
                max-width: 130%;
                height: auto;
                display: block;
                margin: 0 auto;
                animation: jump 2s infinite ease-in-out;
            }

        @@keyframes jump {
            0%, 100% {
                transform: translateY(0);
            }

            50% {
                transform: translateY(-15px);
            }
        }

        .services {
            padding: 50px 0;
            justify-content:center;
            
        }

            .services h2 {
                text-align: center;
                color: #0a3d62;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }

        .service-item {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

            .service-item img {
                height: 80px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

        .testimonials {
            padding: 50px 0;
        }

            .testimonials h2 {
                text-align: center;
                color: #0a3d62;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }

        .testimonial-item {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            margin-right:20px;
        }

            .testimonial-item p {
                font-style: italic;
                color: #555;
            }

            .testimonial-item .author {
                font-weight: bold;
                color: #0a3d62;
            }

        .featured-listings {
            padding: 50px 0;
        }

            .featured-listings h2 {
                text-align: center;
                color: #0a3d62;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }

        .listing-item {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

            .listing-item img {
                width: 100%;
                border-radius: 8px;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
            }

            .listing-item h3 {
                color: #0a3d62;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .listing-item p {
                color: #555;
            }

        .call-to-action {
            padding: 50px 0;
            background-color: #0a3d62;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
        }

            .call-to-action h2 {
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .call-to-action .btn {
                background-color: #1e90ff;
                border: none;
                padding: 10px 20px;
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }

                .call-to-action .btn:hover {
                    background-color: #1c86ee;
                }

        .home-recommendations {
            padding: 50px 0;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #fff;
        }

            .home-recommendations h2 {
                color: #0a3d62;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }

        .recommendation {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-left: -60px;
        }

        .RecoImg img {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .recommendation .info {
            text-align: right;
            margin: 10px;
            justify-content: right;
        }

            .recommendation .info h3 {
                color: #0a3d62;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .recommendation .info p {
                color: #555;
            }

            .recommendation .info button {
                background-color: transparent;
                border: 2px solid #1e90ff;
                border-radius:30px;
                color: #1e90ff;
                padding: 10px 20px;
                font-size: 1rem;
                transition: all 0.3s ease;
                position: relative;
                overflow: hidden;
            }

                .recommendation .info button:hover {
                    background-color: #1e90ff;
                    color: #fff;
                    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(30, 144, 255, 0.6);
                }

                .recommendation .info button::before {
                    content: '';
                    position: absolute;
                    top: -50%;
                    left: -50%;
                    width: 200%;
                    height: 200%;
                    background: rgba(30, 144, 255, 0.2);
                    transform: rotate(45deg);
                    transition: all 0.5s ease;
                    z-index: 1;
                }

                .recommendation .info button:hover::before {
                    top: -20%;
                    left: -20%;
                }

            .BuyImg{
                width:50%;
                margin-left:100px;
                
            }

        .services-item {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 50px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            align-content:center;
            margin-right:20px;
        }
            .services-item p {
                color: #555;
                text-align:center;
            }
            .services-item button{
                align-content:center;
            }
            .services-item h2{
                font-weight:bold;
            }
        .services-btn {
            background-color: transparent;
            border: 2px solid #0026ff;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-left: 90px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding: 5px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            color: #0026ff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
            .services-btn:hover {
                background-color: #0026ff;
                color: #fff;
                box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(30, 144, 255, 0.6);
            }
            .services-btn::before {
                content: '';
                position: absolute;
                top: -50%;
                left: -50%;
                width: 200%;
                height: 200%;
                background: rgba(30, 144, 255, 0.2);
                transform: rotate(45deg);
                transition: all 0.5s ease;
                z-index: 1;
            }
            .services-btn:hover::before {
                top: -20%;
                left: -20%;
            }
        .row {
            --bs-gutter-x: 1.5rem;
            --bs-gutter-y: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: nowrap;
            margin-top: calc(-1* var(--bs-gutter-y));
            margin-right: calc(-0.5* var(--bs-gutter-x));
            margin-left: calc(-0.5* var(--bs-gutter-x));
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h1>Find a place where you can be yourself</h1>
                    <p>If you are looking for a place where you can be yourself, don't give up. Keep searching until you find a place that feels like home.</p>
                    <div class="search-form">
                        <form class="form-inline">
                            <div class="form-group mr-2">
                                <label for="wantTo" class="sr-only">Want to</label>
                                <select class="form-control" id="wantTo">
                                    <option>Buy</option>
                                    <option>Rent</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group mr-2">
                                <label for="propertyType" class="sr-only">Property Type</label>
                                <select class="form-control" id="propertyType">
                                    <optgroup label="Residential">
                                        <option value="apartment" selected>Apartment</option>
                                        <option value="Room">Room</option>
                                        <option value="flat">Flat</option>
                                        <option value="plot">Plot</option>
                                    </optgroup>
                                    <optgroup label="Commercial">
                                        <option value="office">Office</option>
                                        <option value="floor">Floor</option>
                                    </optgroup>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group mr-2">
                                <label for="location" class="sr-only">Location</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="location" placeholder="Street, City, Zip ...">
                            </div>
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Search</button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 gif-container">
                    <img src="~/Content/house.png" alt="Animation">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="home-recommendations">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="recommendation">
                <div class="RecoImg">
                    <img src="~/Content/recom.jpg" alt="Recommended Home" class="recomImage">
                </div>
                <div class="info">
                    <h3>Get home recommendations</h3>
                    <p>Signin for a more personalized experience.</p>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary custom-signin-btn">Sign in</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="services">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4 services-item">
                    <img src="~/Content/buy.jpg" class="BuyImg" />
                    <h2>Buy a home</h2>
                    <p>Find your place with an immersive photo experience and the most listings, including things you won't find anywhere else.</p>
                    <button type="button" class="services-btn">Browse homes</button>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 services-item">
                    <img src="~/Content/sell.jpg" class="BuyImg" />
                    <h2>Sell home</h2>
                    <p>No matter what path you take to sell your home, we can help you navigate a successfull sale.</p>
                    <button type="button" class="services-btn">See your options</button>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 services-item">
                    <img src="~/Content/rent.jpg" class="BuyImg" />
                    <h2>Rent a home</h2>
                    <p>We're creating a seamless online experience - from shopping on the largest rental network, to applying, to paying rent.</p>
                    <button type="button" class="services-btn">Find rentals</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonials">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Testimonials</h2>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4 testimonial-item">
                    <p>"UrbanNest helped me find my dream home quickly and easily. I highly recommend their services!"</p>
                    <p class="author">- Jane Doe</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 testimonial-item">
                    <p>"The team at UrbanNest was professional and knowledgeable. They made the buying process a breeze."</p>
                    <p class="author">- John Smith</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 testimonial-item">
                    <p>"I couldn't be happier with the service I received from UrbanNest. They found the perfect home for me."</p>
                    <p class="author">- Sarah Johnson</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="call-to-action">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Ready to find your dream home?</h2>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="featured-listings">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Featured Listings</h2>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4 listing-item">
                    <img src="~/Content/house1.jpg" alt="House 1">
                    <h3>Modern Apartment</h3>
                    <p>This modern apartment is located in a prime location and features stunning views.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 listing-item">
                    <img src="~/Content/house2.jpg" alt="House 2">
                    <h3>Luxury Villa</h3>
                    <p>This luxury villa offers unparalleled comfort and style, with top-of-the-line amenities.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 listing-item">
                    <img src="~/Content/house3.jpg" alt="House 3">
                    <h3>Cozy Cottage</h3>
                    <p>This cozy cottage is perfect for those looking for a peaceful and charming home.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="text-center py-4">
        <p>&copy; 2024 UrbanNest. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
